    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project car with strong enthusiast appeal. The engine fires up and the car offers a mechanically honest platform with good bones for someone looking for an affordable driver, weekend tinkering build, or parts donor. Cosmetic wear and age-related flaws are present throughout, but the powertrain has character and the chassis still feels like a worthwhile starting point. A great chance to get into a fun, usable car at entry-level money.",
